title: Frigidaire 30in Freestanding Gas Range FFGF3005WH
description:
In this video we take a closer look at the Frigidaire gas range model FFGF3005.  For more details or to place an order please visit us at Abt.com: http://www.abt.com/product/56977/Frigidaire-30-White-Freestanding-Gas-Range-FFGF3005MW.html

Features:
- Even Baking Technology: Our latest technology ensures even baking every time
- Bright Lighting: Our bright lighting makes it easy to see what’s inside
- Color-Coordinated Oven Door with Large Window: Stylish look with a large window makes it easy to check on what’s cooking without opening the door
- Broil and Serve™ Drawer
- Manual Clean Oven
- Black Steel Grates
- Electronic Ignition
- Lift-Up Porcelain Cooktop
- Towel-Bar Handle
- 2 Oven Racks

- Specifications:
Oven Control: Mechanical
Surface Type: Color-Coordinated Porcelain
Grates: Black Square Steel
Window: Large
Exterior Door Finish: Color-Coordinated
Handle Design: Color-Coordinated
Exterior Finish (Side Panels): Color-Coordinated
Oven Cleaning System: Manual Clean
Drawer Functionality: Broil

- Oven Controls:
Bake: Yes
Broil: Yes

- Cooktop:
Right Front Burner (BTU): 9,000
Right Rear Burner (BTU): 9,000
Left Front Burner (BTU): 9,000
Left Rear Burner (BTU): 9,000

- Oven:
Capacity (Cu. Ft.): 4.2
Oven Light: 1
Rack Configuration: 2 Standard
Even Baking System: Yes
Broiling System: Standard
Bake Burner / Broil Burner (BTU): 18,000 / 14,000

- Certifications:
A.D.A. Compliant: Yes

- Electrical:
Power Supply Connection Location: Left Bottom Rear
Gas Supply Connection Location: Right Bottom Rear
Voltage Rating: 120V / 60 Hz / 15A
Connected Load (kW Rating) @ 120 Volts: 1.8
Amps @ 120 Volts: 15

- Approximate Dimensions:
Height: 47-1/2"
Width: 29-7/8"
Depth: 28-1/2"
Depth with Door Open 90°: 46-5/8
Cutout
Height: 33"
Width: 30"
Depth: 24"
